settings.title: About Taylor True Value Rental Center
settings.text:
Tyce Holst has been in the rental business his entire life, and at Taylor Rental since he was 12.  His fine business has been serving West Michigan for over 35 years.

To serve our customers the best that we can, we have a 24 hr. Rental Resolve and Service line for our customers' convenience. 

We service and deliver to many surrounding communities including Grand Haven, South Haven, Saugatuck, Grand Rapids, and Hudsonville.
